data.description: Picturesque turn of the century charm fills this 2-story home. Built in 1900. A great investment opportunity in Interlachen, Florida! Whether you are a seasoned investor looking for your next fix & flip project or just starting your real estate investment journey, don't miss the chance to capitalize on this affordable opportunity today! With the right vision and execution, this property holds the potential for substantial returns through a successful flip or long term hold! This property is being sold AS IS. It is a fixer-upper with great potential on a beautiful lot   The approx. .38 acre lot is home to a number of fruit trees & grape vines plus a great 1-car garage.
